title: 1991 Uganda Cup
text:
1991 <a href="Ugandan%20Cup">Uganda Cup</a> was the 17th season of the main Ugandan <a href="Association%20football">football</a> Cup. 
Overview.
The competition has also been known as the Kakungulu Cup and was won by <a href="Express%20FC">Express Red Eagles</a> who beat <a href="Nile%20Breweries%20FC">Nile Breweries FC</a> 4-1 in the final. The results are not available for the earlier rounds
